title: VOLTE ISSUE
content:
https://support.google.com/pixelphone/thread/46575489?hl=en#

I already asked. But it isn't help.

Hardware is supported, but not software.  
Because pixel is not released in Kor.
It is solved when I insert these 2 lines.

When nexus released in Kor, device support TTA-VOLTE. 
But pixel doesn't support TTA-VOLTE. Because pixel doesn't contain supporting code. 
These 2 lines can trigger supporting TTA-VOLTE.
